BTree
Class BNode

java.lang.Object
  BTree.BNode
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class BNode
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

This class is for a BNode. BNodes are used in the BTree class. A BNode has an ArrayList of the keys, and Arraylist of child BNodes, a parent BNode, the order of the node, the BNode that's to the right of this node, and the maximum number of children and the maximum number of keys

May, Bill
